headline: Automakers were busy in 2024. Here's what's next in 2025.
summary: General Motors (GM), Ford (F), and Stellantis (STLA) all had an eventful 2024, leaving each company with looming questions about what's to come in the new year. Yahoo Finance’s Pras Subramanian joins Akiko Fujita and Josh Lipton on Market Domination Overtime to recap 2024 automotive industry performance and discuss what potential policy changes under President-elect Trump's second term could mean for the industry in 2025. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here. This post was written by Josh Lynch
